  <ModelName>Preferred assignment to single-skill or multi-skill operators</ModelName>
  <ModelDescription>In call center environments in particular, the question often arises as to whether incoming calls should be routed
primarily to a suitable single-skill agent or a multi-skill agent (if both are currently available). Single-skill
agents are generally faster—however, routing calls to a multi-skill agent avoids the need for potential transfers
that might otherwise be necessary. Which strategy is better in each case depends on the actual numerical values
for the factors mentioned.</ModelDescription>
